Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一份是嗎  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝小姐惠顧囉～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小澪啊  要炒麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是正式演出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去抓緊練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  雖然我也想去練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是班裡早市值班的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又跳閘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  又跳了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要炒生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這都第幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  電磁爐只能開三台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有遵守嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們啦  不是五班她們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼不相信我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也挺不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧  請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  律  正式出演前不再練習一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉  現在脫不開身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  隊伍都排這麼長了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能找個人頂一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個計劃的提案人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不先做點表率說不過去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那紬在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺挺不錯的  沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  班裡的人直接進去就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較黑  要小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬…紬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  紬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬！
