Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你那聲音沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動中練過頭罷了  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是你們第一次登台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是下午三點開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還算有些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再練習一下嗎
