Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  接著就交給我吧
