Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪她們呢
