Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還有點嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說句「多謝款待」看看
