Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位請！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都在練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了  澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你一個人練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來練習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太磨蹭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還不賴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很完美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照剛才的感覺來吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不情願  但既然是輕音社的顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想著是不是有我能幫忙的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們做了衣服哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠來勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  老師  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是很感激你的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿著那種衣服唱歌嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是在那麼多人面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似時機稍微差了點吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不合你們意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我以前的衣服怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是想穿剛才那套衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種衣服就算不是澪也會覺得害羞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…虧我這麼努力做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我看小唯她們可是穿得很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你們兩個！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  怎麼會是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在緊張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我幫你化妝得連你自己都認不出來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  正式演出加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我把之前的東西都忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習吧  現在只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒發生  什麼也沒發生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…哈…哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把這個拿到大禮堂去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重的  小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  說來小澪她人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  澪正在做別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主唱…要在很多人面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她來肯定會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太讓人擔心了  不敢讓她搬東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一滴汗都沒流…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sha-lan-la  sha-lan-la～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（シャランラ：出自動畫「魔女ッ子メグちゃん」的台詞\N順帶一提此動畫播出年份為1974年）\N（Rcat：另外手中的雅馬哈…你又問爺爺要器材啦紬紬XXD）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  唯  現在正在演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那個放在一邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是合唱社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下來是輕音社…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  器材已經搬來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～終於搬完啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位  茶泡好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律和小澪是從小一起長大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始在一起的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是從幼稚園就在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？還是小學來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一起長大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪她小時候就很怕羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好漂亮的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了這麼一句…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！原來你是左撇子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽我說！小澪她可厲害了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就羞得滿臉通紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那根本就是怪小律你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器材已經搬完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  看起來挺冷靜的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼不想做主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直這麼緊張下去嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明緊張得一塌糊塗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要來真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣子怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  你代我做主唱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰來敲鼓啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來替你敲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那貝司呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也我來做！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你個頭啊！你做一個我看看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律～律～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離遠點！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  小澪  都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是聲音沒變成這樣的話  小澪就不用做主唱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是我來做主唱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  還要想下MC呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？自我介紹之類啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  演唱會的時候每曲之間不是要講話的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家今天來聽我們輕音社的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來由我來介紹樂隊成員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假日裡總是無所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜點總能吃個一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠哉哉小妖精  平澤  唯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍵盤手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在點心的品味上出類拔萃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖巧執著的天然系大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴吹  紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝司兼主唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平生最怕恐怖和痛苦的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社的焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Dangerous Queen{\fsp115}　{\r}\N危險女王  秋山  澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰Dangerous啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後則是我  鼓手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰雪聰明  八面玲瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著陽光一般的微笑為大家傳遞幸福的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中  律！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把自己捧到天上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗆到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝合唱社的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一次舞台演出！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是展現我們練習成果的時候了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要我穿成這樣出演才行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很配你哦  小澪澪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個節目是輕音樂社為大家帶來的樂隊演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！大家上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  唯
